317
00:46:42,397 --> 00:46:46,766
Me ajuda! Por favor! Por favor!

318
00:46:59,014 --> 00:47:01,539
Vamos! Vamos!

319
00:47:15,697 --> 00:47:17,426
Rose!

320
00:47:19,034 --> 00:47:20,763
Sharon!

321
00:47:24,539 --> 00:47:26,598
Rose!

322
00:48:30,305 --> 00:48:31,897
Rose!

323
00:48:42,817 --> 00:48:44,512
Rose.

