833
01:41:20,760 --> 01:41:23,058
Por quê?

834
01:41:24,898 --> 01:41:27,833
Queime a bruxa! Queime ela!

835
01:41:28,034 --> 01:41:33,131
Queime a bruxa! Queima ela!
Queime a bruxa!

836
01:41:40,180 --> 01:41:41,977
Sharon.

837
01:41:49,222 --> 01:41:51,247
Bruxa maligna!

838
01:41:52,192 --> 01:41:54,183
Sofra.

839
01:41:58,631 --> 01:42:01,259
Queime a bruxa! Queime ela!

840
